name: Vessels 144: SAVAGE STEVE
description: The origins of Steve’s nickname are unclear, but most people who now him believe it derives from one of two possible incidents. Either the time when Steve was at a dinner party and he made a remark about a fellow guest’s outfit that was so cutting the that other guest was forced to make their excuses and leave before dessert, OR the time Steve allowed himself to be swallowed alive by an rampaging Exolizard and proceeded to tear his way out from the inside with his bare hands.
